              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "12": {
                  "id": "12",
                  "speaker": "Narrator",
                  "text": "*The letter is written in Elminster's crabbed hand. And, given his usual verbosity, is rather succinct...*",
                  "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Gale reads the letter (looking down at it, doesn't have to be shown)",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "3": {
                      "id": "3",
                      "speaker": "Weary Traveller",
                      "text": "I see remaining optimistic as my duty - especially when I am not the one being asked to do the seemingly impossible.",
                      "context": "NodeContext: hint of regret",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "8": {
                          "id": "8",
                          "speaker": "Weary Traveller",
                          "text": "Think carefully - exceedingly so. You know Mystra, as do I. I was not born an old man. I am all too familiar with what it's like to have a goddess fill your heart with longing.",
                          "context": "NodeContext: hint of regret",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "29": {
                              "id": "29",
                              "speaker": "Weary Traveller",
                              "text": "If there is another way, I trust you can find it. It is not in your nature or mine to stop looking, to accept the first answer to any dilemma. Do what you can - put that mind to work.",
                              "context": "NodeContext: hint of regret",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "5": {
                                  "id": "5",
                                  "speaker": "Weary Traveller",
                                  "text": "Perhaps... perhaps that should have been your mission right from the start.",
                                  "context": "NodeContext: hint of regret",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "10": {
                                      "id": "10",
                                      "speaker": "Narrator",
                                      "text": "*Reading between Elminster's cramped lines, you can draw only one conclusion. He thinks you should defy Mystra's instruction, and refuse to use the orb.*",
                                      "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Gale stops reading, a look of mild concern on his face",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "",
                                      "is_end": false,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {
                                        "9": {
                                          "id": "9",
                                          "speaker": "Tara the Tressym",
                                          "text": "What is it, darling? You look rather pale.",
                                          "context": "NodeContext: suddenly tender with worry.",
                                          "checkflags": [],
                                          "setflags": [],
                                          "ruletags": [],
                                          "approval": [],
                                          "rolls": "",
                                          "goto": "",
                                          "link": "",
                                          "is_end": false,
                                          "node_type": "normal",
                                          "children": {
                                            "13": {
                                              "id": "13",
                                              "speaker": "Player",
                                              "text": "Elminster's changed his tune. He thinks I shouldn't use the orb.",
                                              "context": "NodeContext: like 'yeah right'",
                                              "checkflags": [],
                                              "setflags": [],
                                              "ruletags": [],
                                              "approval": [],
                                              "rolls": "",
                                              "goto": "",
                                              "link": "",
                                              "is_end": false,
                                              "node_type": "normal",
                                              "children": {
                                                "11": {
                                                  "id": "11",
                                                  "speaker": "Tara the Tressym",
                                                  "text": "Aha! Mr Aumar can always be relied upon to bring a dash of good sense to proceedings. A shame he didn't start with that, but still.",
                                                  "context": "",
                                                  "checkflags": [],
                                                  "setflags": [],
                                                  "ruletags": [],
                                                  "approval": [],
                                                  "rolls": "",
                                                  "goto": "",
                                                  "link": "",
                                                  "is_end": false,
                                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                                  "children": {
                                                    "17": {
                                                      "id": "17",
                                                      "speaker": "Tara the Tressym",
                                                      "text": "I hope you plan to heed his advice. Carefully, though. He seemed rather fidgety when he delivered his message. Mystra will have both of you in her bad books before long.",
                                                      "context": "",
                                                      "checkflags": [],
                                                      "setflags": [],
                                                      "ruletags": [],
                                                      "approval": [],
                                                      "rolls": "",
                                                      "goto": "",
